| **Can early biomarkers predict durable benefit?** | $3M | ctDNA kinetic model enabling future patient selection |
| **What infrastructure enables Phase 2 scale-up?** | $2M | Operational learnings, data platform, regulatory pathway |

**Key Message:** This isn't a $32M trial. It's a **$32M knowledge platform** that generates multiple datasets of lasting value to the field.

