- Drug costs reduce by $3.75M
- Reallocation options:
  - Expand to 40-45 patients (increase power)
  - Add deeper immune profiling (TCR sequencing, single-cell RNA-seq)
  - Extend follow-up to 24 months
  - Build reserve for Phase 2 planning

**If ctDNA partnership secured at deeper discount:**
- Save additional $1M
- Could enable patient-specific assays for all patients (not just subset)

